Jonathan Groff on the Time He Disagreed With Producers on David Fincher's 'Mindhunter'|http://www.variety.com/videos|https://variety.com/video/jonathan-groff-on-the-time-he-disagreed-with-producers-on-david-finchers-mindhunter/||2018-06-12|Variety Staff||While talking with Maggie Gyllenhaal (“The Deuce”) for Variety’s “Actors on Actors,” presented by Shutterstock, Jonathan Groff (“Mindhunter”) revealed that during the shooting of the 10-episode span of David Fincher’s “Mindhunter,” he fought to include a certain version of a scene.
